Category:  General  Topic:  practice



This is how you gain the ability to do skills and spells.  A guildmaster
of your class must be presesnt to teach you.  If given no arguments, practice
will show you what you already know.

Syntax:  practice [spell/skill] <<i_th> [teacher]>

Example:  practice illumminate		Teaches you illuminate
	  practice			Same as 'abilities'.

See Also:  abilities, score
